  <skill Name="斧头" Class="Axe" Description="斧头专精" Cost="50" Attribute="Strength" Snippet="the axe" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_axe.png" Foreground="y" Detail="R">
    <power Name="斧头熟练度" Cost="0" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="0" Class="Axe_Expertise" Snippet="the axe" Description="用斧头攻击获得 +2" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_axe_proficiency.png" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
    <power Name="劈开" Cost="150" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="19" Class="Axe_Cleave" Snippet="cleaving" Description="用斧头击中对手时, 有75%的几率切割对方的护甲, 使他们的AV受到-1的惩罚. 这种惩罚可以叠加多次, 最高可达Strength修正值的一半. 最高时, 暴击+1." Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_cleave.png" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
    <power Name="冲锋攻击" Cost="100" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="19" Class="Cudgel_ChargingStrike" Prereq="Axe_Cleave,Tactics_Charge" Snippet="charging and striking" Description="用斧头冲锋并命中时, 如果切割了敌人的护甲, 他们的AV会受到额外-1的惩罚. 如果你有肢解, 用斧头冲锋时肢解的几率会增加一倍. 用棍棒冲锋并击中对手时, 会使对手晕眩." Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_axe_charging_strike.png" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
    <power Name="肢解" Cost="150" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="21" Class="Axe_Dismember" Snippet="dismembering" Description="激活;冷却时间30. 斧的攻击. 如果击中并穿透, 随机肢解对手的一条肢体, 使其开始流血(每回合1-2点伤害, Tou大于35可豁免). 此外, 斧头攻击穿透有一定的肢解几率:单手斧3%,双手斧6%" Tile="Abilities/abil_dismember.bmp" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
    <power Name="斧头钩击" Cost="150" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="23" Class="Axe_HookAndDrag" Snippet="hooking and dragging" Description="激活,冷却时间50. 用斧头的后跟抓住对手的四肢. 如果成功,在移动时拉住对手, 并攻击一次. 对手有机会抵抗该移动(Strength豁免;难度20+Str修正), 并有机会在回合开始时挣脱(相同的豁免). 持续9回合或直到你肢解对手" Tile="Abilities/abil_hook_and_drag.bmp" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
    <power Name="斩头" Cost="150" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="25" Class="Axe_Decapitate" Prereq="Axe_Dismember" Snippet="decapitating" Description="你可以肢解的肢体中增加了头部. 砍掉一个生物唯一的头会让他们立刻丧命. 如果该生物有多个头部,它们开始大量流血(每回合造成2-3点伤害,韧性豁免:35)." Tile="Abilities/abil_decapitate_toggle_off.bmp" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
    <power Name="狂暴!" Cost="300" Attribute="Strength" Minimum="29" Class="Axe_Berserk" Prereq="Axe_Dismember" Snippet="going berserk" Description="激活;冷却时间100.
你进入一个血腥狂乱状态, 在5轮内斧头攻击肢解的几率是100%. 要使用狂暴,肢解必须不在CD,使用狂暴会使肢解进入CD." Tile="Abilities/abil_berserk.bmp" Foreground="y" Detail="R"></power>
  </skill>

  <skill Name="弓和步枪" Class="Rifles" Description="弓箭和步枪专精" Cost="100" Attribute="Agility" Snippet="the bow and the rifle" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_bow_and_rifle.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B">
    <power Name="稳定之手" Cost="0" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="19" Class="Rifle_SteadyHands" Snippet="the bow and the rifle" Description="确保使用弓箭和步枪的精度, Agility被视为高了4点" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_steady_hand.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="目标标记" Cost="0" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="19" Class="Rifle_DrawABead" Snippet="drawing a bead" Description="用一个标记对手, 当用弓或步枪射击有标记的目标时, Agility+2. 一次只能标记一个目标, 如果看不见目标, 标记就会消失" Tile="Abilities/abil_mark_target.bmp" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="压制火力" Cost="150" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="19" Class="Rifle_SuppressiveFire" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead" Snippet="suppressive fire" Description="当向一个有标记的目标射击时, 如果射击穿透, 目标将被压制, 不能移动3-5回合. 压制后标记移除" Tile="Abilities/tile_supressive_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="碾压火力" Cost="200" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="25" Class="Rifle_FlatteningFire" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead,Rifle_SuppressiveFire" Snippet="flattening fire" Description="如果目标被6个或更多的固体障碍物包围, 压制火力就会升级为碾压火力, 碾压火力会使目标趴下并解除他们的武装." Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_flattening_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="伤害之火" Cost="150" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="19" Class="Rifle_WoundingFire" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead" Snippet="wounding fire" Description="向被标记的目标射击时，每一发命中，你的目标每轮损失1点伤害(豁免:20 + 武器最大伤害)。然后移除标记" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_wounding_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="迷惑之火" Cost="200" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="25" Class="Rifle_DisorientingFire" Snippet="disorienting fire" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead,Rifle_WoundingFire" Description="只要你的目标看不到或听不到任何阵营盟友，伤害之火就会升级为迷惑之火。迷惑之火还会使目标的DV和MA减4。" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_disorienting_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="真火" Cost="150" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="19" Class="Rifle_SureFire" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead" Snippet="sure fire" Description="向一个有标记的目标开火，没有精度惩罚(武器的精度仍然很重要)。然后移除标记。" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_sure_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="信标之火" Cost="200" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="25" Class="Rifle_BeaconFire" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead,Rifle_SureFire" Snippet="beacon fire" Description="当目标是燃烧的、发光的或磷光的，“真火”就升级为“信标之火”。信标之火射击也被视为暴击。" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_beacon_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
    <power Name="终极开火" Cost="300" Attribute="Agility" Minimum="29" Class="Rifle_OneShot" Prereq="Rifle_DrawABead" Snippet="ultra fire" Description="冷却时间100。向一个有标记的目标射击。射击结合了所有其他火焰技能的效果。" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_ultra_fire.png" Foreground="y" Detail="B"></power>
