    <power Name="烹饪增强" Cost="50" Attribute="Intelligence" Minimum="17" Class="CookingAndGathering_Spicer" Snippet="spicing" Description="当你选择烹饪材料时，你最多可以选择三种而不是两种。用三种食材烹饪的饭菜会赋予更强大的地位效应。" Tile="Abilities/sw_skill_spicer.png" Foreground="y" Detail="r"></power>
